  "texts": [
    "The share of the world gross domestic product from 7% to 12% (in developed countries) falls on the construction industry, which shows how important it is to ensure sustainable innovative development of this industry.",
    "Today, in many countries with a developed construction industry, attention is mainly paid to the implementation of innovation policy and the formation of a national innovation system.",
    "Also, priority attention is paid to financial and organizational issues of the development of the construction industry.Large-scale research to ensure sustainable innovative development in the construction industry is carried out around the world.",
    "In the conditions of innovative development of the economy, the building complex, which is the most important stage of the investment and construction process, is becoming increasingly popular.Therefore, the activation of the innovation process in this area ensures the timely commissioning of capital construction facilities, the development of production and an increase in efficiency.",
    "The development of the processes of globalization, innovation and international integration has led to the regulation of the types of innovation and the creation of international standards."
  ],
